會遊行的上訴機制。潘官認為，相關議題極為重要和複雜，需要小心處理，對日後集會自由影響深遠，又估計本案將在終審法院處理。</blockquote><br />\n呢段又係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n818和平到咁撚樣都要告<br />\n仲吹到有保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />告入左姐係當日170萬人都入得，全部都有資格申請政治庇護"},{"pid":"0c94a8e3bd81bd82c5e0d899bc061af356548813","tid":2363411,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"[143日] 十二港人案  聽日年紀最細嘅手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2363596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2363596</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"160f3b3118fe988998d35e9041345e0fd1a4cce4","tid":2363411,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"律政屍唔爭在要求判死刑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399bb8af1c150893e732b22bebe9baefd8cceb80","tid":2363411,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"係英國係咪應該搞搞呢條狀棍"},{"pid":"2e9d223d981bc27a155d943d5d1d642988609e9f","tid":2363411,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"搵人寫信去英國大律師公會投訴佢"},{"pid":"0a321b9b124a8d20edd8703a6766561e9fa59e87","tid":2363411,"uid":113065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:35:13.000Z","msg":"律政司重金聘<span class=\"red\">英</span>御用大状已犯国安法"},{"pid":"c8482e09d722d862fa627703b10e8a67bebe739c","tid":2363411,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"搵個鬼佬返嚟就扮公平審訊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"756fbde82ed0b5820a06cc270a1f95606a98ecd3","tid":2363411,"uid":240362,"like":0,"disli